 DeepRecursiveScope. Maybe I can also search the repository to see if it’s already in use.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_asbEFexVAQz66eXVlmvlx5bz|fc_02495e0ba1f28d900169efa3b1a88c819c97181070353aefe6", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "rg -n \"DeepRecursiveFunction|DeepRecursiveScope\" tests/src metadata -S", "timeout": 10}, "partialJson": "{\"command\":\"rg -n \\\"DeepRecursiveFunction|DeepRecursiveScope\\\" tests/src metadata -S\",\"timeout\":10}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.4", "usage": {"input": 398, "output": 1153, "cacheRead": 13312, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 14863, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777312665255, "responseId": "resp_02495e0ba1f28d900169efa399c610819cb82e2a5cf53b8f92"}}
